Package API

package API
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    ApiClient
    The ApiClient class is used to send http requests to AeroAPI for real-time flight data including scheduled departures, airport lists, and airline operator names in JSON format.
    FlightController
    The FlightController is used to make specific API calls to the ApiClient class Type of API calls include scheduled departures, airport lists, and airline operators.
    FlightModel
    The model for flight data and blueprint that molds incoming API data.
